3 h\u1ea1n, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc t\u1ea1i TP.HCM.  Hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Weaver 200 v\u00e0 Weaver++ t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ea1c nhanh n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam.jpg\" title=\"1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672427889_83_dat-bike-weaver-xe-may-dien-made-in-vietnam.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u1ede Weaver++, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e1nh sau b\u1eb1ng nh\u00f4ng x\u00edch, x\u00edch v\u00e0 phu\u1ed9c thay v\u00ec g\u1eafn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c b\u00e1nh xe nh\u01b0 Weaver ho\u1eb7c Weaver 200. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u0103ng th\u00eam 1 kW, l\u00ean 7 kW (9,3 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c) ).  ), kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a xe t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.  B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa b\u00e1nh sau (v\u00ed d\u1ee5: x\u1eb9p l\u1ed1p) kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u1ede Weaver++, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u01