 ch\u1ecbu t\u1ea3i cho xe.  Dat Bike Weaver++ \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m pin).  H\u00e3ng k\u00edch c\u1ea7u ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft khi gi\u1ea3m ngay 1 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi mua xe trong th\u00e1ng 12.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, Weaver++ kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  T\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu xe \u0111i\u1ec7n Dat Bike c\u00f3 th\u00eam l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 VinFast Theon gi\u00e1 63,9-69,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu mua xe k\u00e8m pin (17,2 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng), gi\u00e1 Theon t\u0103ng l\u00ean 81,1-87,1 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 gi\u1eefa c\u0169ng gi\u00fap tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Weaver++ c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m.  G\u1eafp sau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay g\u1eafp m\u1edbi c\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ea3i cho xe.  Dat Bike Weaver++ \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m pin).  H\u00e3ng k\u00edch c\u1ea7u ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft khi gi\u1ea3m ngay 1 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi mua xe trong th\u00e1ng 12.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, Weaver++ kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  T\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu xe \u0111i\u1ec7n Dat Bike c\u00f3 th\u00eam l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 VinFast Theon gi\u00e1 63,9-69,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu mua xe k\u00e8m pin (17,2 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng), gi\u00e1 Theon t\u0103ng l\u00ean 81,1-87,1 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Weaver++ c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 65,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t trong b\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Dat Bike nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t, n\u1eb1m \u1edf ghi \u0111\u00f4ng, phu\u1ed9c, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1\u2026 Weaver++ l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe th\u1ee9 ba trong d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Dat Bike, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u xe m\u00e1y \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f2n non tr\u1ebb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. So [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17076,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18053"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18053"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18053\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/17076"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18053"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18053"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18053"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}